bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.menu

  • Packages that use bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.menu 
    Package Description
    bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.menu  
  • Classes in bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.menu used by bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.menu 
    Class and Description
    AbstractCustomizationMenu
    The abstract implementation of CustomizationMenu offers fields to store standard data required by all menus.
    CustomizationMenu
    A CustomizationMenu is a menu that is shown belonging to a ToolbarGroupDockStation, the menu can offer various settings to customize the station.
    Clients should call CustomizationMenu.setController(DockController) and CustomizationMenu.setContent(CustomizationMenuContent) to set up the menu.
    CustomizationMenuCallback
    This callback is delivered to a CustomizationMenu, it allows the menu to communicate with its parent DockStation.
    CustomizationMenuContent
    A CustomizationMenuContent is a part of the CustomizationMenu.
    CustomizationToolbarButton
    The CustomizationToolbarButton is a button that allows to add one Dockable to a DockStation.
    CustomizationToolbarButton.ItemLocation
    The different locations where a Dockable can be in respect to this button
    GroupedCustomizationMenuContent.Group
    One group of CustomizationMenuContents
